manifests.contents:
bench = []
test = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "rust-calories-tracker"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
required-features = []

[package]
name = "rust-calories-tracker"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true

[dependencies]
async-recursion = "1.0.2"
axum = "0.6.4"
axum-macros = "0.3.2"
dotenv = "0.15.0"
futures = "0.3.26"
itertools = "0.10.5"
mongodb = "2.3.1"
serde_with = "2.2.0"
strum_macros = "0.24.3"
thiserror = "1.0.38"
tokio-stream = "0.1.11"
tracing = "0.1.37"

[dependencies.bson]
version = "2.5.0"
features = ["chrono-0_4", "serde_with", "uuid-1"]

[dependencies.chrono]
version = "0.4.19"
features = ["serde"]

[dependencies.clap]
version = "4.1.4"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.118"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.strum]
version = "0.24.1"
features = ["strum_macros"]

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.25.0"
features = ["full"]

[dependencies.tower]
version = "0.4.13"
features = ["full"]

[dependencies.tower-http]
version = "0.3.5"
features = ["full"]

[dependencies.tracing-subscriber]
version = "0.3.16"
features = ["env-filter"]

[dependencies.uuid]
version = "1.3.0"
features = ["serde", "v4", "macro-diagnostics"]
